chan = Rails.configuration.slack_channels.horizons_crux

header "🌌 welcome to crux!"

section <<~TEXT, markdown: true
  You've just been added to <##{chan}>, the channel for Horizons Crux in Australia! For more info, check out [horizons.hackclub.com/crux](https://horizons.hackclub.com/crux).

  Head over and introduce yourself!
TEXT
